<h2 id="Userstory:Notifications-Primaryuserstory">
  Primary user story
</h2>
As a user, I want to view notifications about what&#39;s happening with my work, so that I can stay up to date on progress.







<h2 id="Userstory:Notifications-Requirements">
  Requirements
</h2>
<table>
  <colgroup>
    <col/>
    <col/>
    <col/>
    <col/>
    <col/>
    <col/>
  </colgroup>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <th>
        #
      </th>
      <th>
        Title
      </th>
      <th>
        User Story
      </th>
      <th colspan="1">
        JIRA Issues
      </th>
      <th>
        Notes
      </th>
      <th colspan="1">
        Importance
      </th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>
        1
      </td>
      <td>
        View notifications
      </td>
      <td>
        As a user, I want to see a stream of notifications about page edits, creations, and comments so that I can stay up to date.
      </td>
      <td colspan="1">
        <img src="https://templates.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/33679/sof-54.png?api=v2">
      </td>
      <td>
        Sort the notifications chronologically, with the most recent on top.
      </td>
      <td colspan="1">
        MUST HAVE
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td colspan="1">
        2
      </td>
      <td colspan="1">
        Push notifications
      </td>
      <td colspan="1">
        As a user, I want to be notified in real time when changes happen on Confluence so that I can respond quickly.
      </td>
      <td colspan="1">
        <img src="https://templates.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/33679/sof-55.png?api=v2">
      </td>
      <td colspan="1">
        We should batch notifications that are similar.
      </td>
      <td colspan="1">
        MUST HAVE
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td colspan="1">
        3
      </td>
      <td colspan="1">
        Timestamp
      </td>
      <td colspan="1">
        As a user, I want to see the timestamp of notifications so that I know when they arrived.
      </td>
      <td colspan="1">
        <img src="https://templates.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/33679/sof-56.png?api=v2">
      </td>
      <td colspan="1">
        Use the format day - month - year.
      </td>
      <td colspan="1">
        NICE TO HAVE
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td colspan="1">
        4
      </td>
      <td colspan="1">
        Avatar
      </td>
      <td colspan="1">
        As a user, I want to see a picture of the person that did the work that caused a notification so that I know who did the action.
      </td>
      <td colspan="1">
        <img src="https://templates.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/33679/sof-57.png?api=v2">
      </td>
      <td colspan="1">
        Can we use rounded avatars?
      </td>
      <td colspan="1">
        NICE TO HAVE
      </td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
